[1986]

13
00:04:30,510 --> 00:04:31,120
Qu Tong,

14
00:04:31,430 --> 00:04:32,480
tell me,

15
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,680
did you write

16
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:35,000
these two names?

17
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,960
I didn't. It wasn't me.

18
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,510
She did it. She's lying.

19
00:04:40,050 --> 00:04:42,110
[Teacher's Office]

20
00:04:52,630 --> 00:04:53,270
Move aside.

21
00:04:53,270 --> 00:04:54,730
She's coming. Step aside.

22
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:55,830
Step aside.

23
00:04:55,830 --> 00:04:56,960
Don't block her way.

24
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:57,510
Make way.

25
00:04:57,510 --> 00:04:58,840
Step aside. Step aside.

26
00:04:59,120 --> 00:04:59,780
Step aside.

27
00:05:05,390 --> 00:05:06,160
Ms. Shen,

28
00:05:06,190 --> 00:05:07,240
you're finally here.

29
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,390
This is Hao Meili's mother,

30
00:05:08,390 --> 00:05:09,630
and this is Hao Meili.

31
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,920
You're Qu Tong's mother, right?

32
00:05:14,070 --> 00:05:16,070
How do you even raise your daughter?

33
00:05:16,750 --> 00:05:18,310
Today we need

34
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:20,040
to clear this up right here.

35
00:05:20,510 --> 00:05:21,710
Or I won't let this go.

36
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:23,920
Did you do it?

37
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:25,430
Mom, I didn't do it.

38
00:05:27,390 --> 00:05:28,040
Ms. Zhang.

39
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:30,720
You're saying Qu Tong did it,

40
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,640
but do you have any evidence?

41
00:05:34,630 --> 00:05:36,360
This is the evidence.

42
00:05:37,050 --> 00:05:38,570
[Qu Tong, the prettiest in the class]
[Hao Meili, the ugliest in the class]

43
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,920
This is the evidence?

44
00:05:42,390 --> 00:05:43,680
Everything is blurry.

45
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:46,480
What do you mean by that?

46
00:05:47,070 --> 00:05:48,310
Your daughter did it!

47
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:50,040
No one else but her.

48
00:05:50,190 --> 00:05:51,040
It was her.

49
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,810
What are you looking at?

50
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,070
Ms. Zhang.

51
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,480
What we've been taught tells us

52
00:05:56,750 --> 00:05:57,920
that for anything we do,

53
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,270
we must base it on reason and evidence,

54
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:00,480
and seek truth from facts.

55
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,340
This principle

56
00:06:01,510 --> 00:06:03,370
holds wherever we go, doesn't it?

57
00:06:03,950 --> 00:06:04,750
Ms. Zhang.

58
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,130
I wonder

59
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,620
what you think about this.

60
00:06:08,430 --> 00:06:08,750
Yes.

61
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,210
Coming here to show off to me

62
00:06:10,210 --> 00:06:11,870
that you're educated, right?

63
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:12,560
So you're educated,

64
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,800
what's so great about that?

65
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,390
You still raised a daughter like this.

66
00:06:15,390 --> 00:06:17,310
She's just embarrassing herself here.

67
00:06:17,310 --> 00:06:18,950
I may not be well-educated,

68
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,860
but my daughter is a good student.

69
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,660
Unbelievable.

70
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:25,040
Mrs. Shi, please don't be angry.

71
00:06:25,430 --> 00:06:26,120
Ms. Shen

72
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,950
certainly didn't mean it that way.

73
00:06:27,950 --> 00:06:28,630
Right now,

74
00:06:28,630 --> 00:06:29,480
we truly don't have

75
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,720
sufficient evidence to prove

76
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,380
that the writing

77
00:06:31,380 --> 00:06:32,440
was done by Qu Tong.

78
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,390
Of course, this incident has gone too far.

79
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:36,000
Our school will never tolerate phenomena

80
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,659
like students judging others

81
00:06:37,830 --> 00:06:38,950
by their appearance

82
00:06:38,950 --> 00:06:39,750
or bullying.

83
00:06:40,310 --> 00:06:41,770
Wait, what are you saying?

84
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,870
So Meili suffered for nothing?

85
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:45,510
My daughter transferred here,

86
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:48,040
and she can't score better
than my daughter.

87
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,120
It's obvious!

88
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:49,870
So,

89
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:50,750
she just

90
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,159
used something like this

91
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:53,360
to bully my daughter?

92
00:06:53,390 --> 00:06:55,120
You're way too mean!

93
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,680
Ms. Zhang.

94
00:06:58,310 --> 00:06:59,430
Now I get it.

95
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,159
There's no evidence at all,

96
00:07:01,159 --> 00:07:01,750
right?

97
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,570
It's all just speculation.

98
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,270
Are you trying to weasel out of this?

99
00:07:06,270 --> 00:07:07,930
You think we're soft targets,

100
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:09,150
easy to bully, right?

101
00:07:09,510 --> 00:07:10,120
Ms. Zhang,

102
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,040
you can't resolve this, can you?

103
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:11,310
Please

104
00:07:11,310 --> 00:07:12,750
get the principal here right now.

105
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:13,720
I demand an explanation today.

106
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:14,780
Or this isn't over.

107
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,040
Ms. Zhang.

108
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,760
I'm quite busy with work.

109
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:18,630
Let's do this.

110
00:07:18,630 --> 00:07:20,240
Qu Tong will come back with me first.

111
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,430
Once I find out more
about what's going on,

112
00:07:21,430 --> 00:07:22,600
we can talk further.

113
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:23,160
Okay.

114
00:07:23,270 --> 00:07:24,360
You can go back first then.

115
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:24,750
Okay.

116
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:25,950
Wait, Ms. Zhang.

117
00:07:25,950 --> 00:07:26,600
What do you mean?

118
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,750
We're not done here.

119
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:28,830
How dare you leave?

120
00:07:28,830 --> 00:07:29,310
Hold on.

121
00:07:29,750 --> 00:07:30,680
What do you mean?

122
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,360
You haven't even sorted this out yet.

123
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:33,890
What are you doing?

124
00:07:33,890 --> 00:07:35,000
Come here, sit down,

125
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:36,430
Explain everything to me.

126
00:07:36,430 --> 00:07:37,470
Sit here. Don't be afraid.

127
00:07:37,470 --> 00:07:38,250
I'm here with you.

128
00:07:38,250 --> 00:07:42,280
[Yunzhou No.1 High School]

129
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:51,560
Mom.

130
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,460
I really...

131
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,120
That Qu Tong,

132
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:25,310
[Mediation Room]

133
00:08:22,270 --> 00:08:23,510
she's the one

134
00:08:23,540 --> 00:08:25,280
who hurt my daughter, you know?

135
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:27,430
Then he dragged me here.

136
00:08:28,830 --> 00:08:29,560
You...

137
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,040
Come in.

138
00:08:32,070 --> 00:08:33,160
Qu Tong!

139
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:35,830
Listen to me.

140
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,299
You pay attention.

141
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:39,110
As long as I'm alive,

142
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:42,440
as long as I'm breathing,
I won't let you off.

143
00:08:42,909 --> 00:08:43,870
You hear me?

144
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:47,720
Mrs. Shi.

145
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:49,860
Today I'm going

146
00:08:49,860 --> 00:08:51,260
to tell you very clearly.

147
00:08:52,150 --> 00:08:53,600
Whatever happened to Shi Yue

148
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:55,400
had nothing to do with me before,

149
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:57,280
and has nothing to do with me now.

150
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,860
Nothing to do with you?

151
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:01,150
Then who is responsible?

152
00:09:01,170 --> 00:09:01,960
Shi Muxian!

153
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,500
You think I don't know anything,

154
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:09,140
right?

155
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:11,510
Your relationship with Su Muxin

156
00:09:11,550 --> 00:09:13,150
has been bad for a long time.

157
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,910
He doesn't even go home.

158
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:16,790
He abandoned you.

159
00:09:16,810 --> 00:09:17,920
He didn't want you.

160
00:09:18,390 --> 00:09:20,440
So you hated Meili, right?

161
00:09:20,550 --> 00:09:21,960
So you hurt her.

162
00:09:23,390 --> 00:09:24,670
So you killed her,

163
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:25,930
didn't you?

164
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,200
Say something!

165
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,320
Yes, you're right.

166
00:09:29,550 --> 00:09:32,030
My relationship with him
has indeed been bad.

167
00:09:32,030 --> 00:09:33,440
But do you know why?

168
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:35,720
Because I lost interest

169
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,910
in him long ago.

170
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:39,530
I actually hoped Hao Meili

171
00:09:39,530 --> 00:09:41,330
would take him away completely.

172
00:09:42,670 --> 00:09:43,550
All her life,

173
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,290
she has been so useless.

174
00:09:56,630 --> 00:09:57,630
Is that Zhou Mi?

175
00:09:57,630 --> 00:09:58,690
Is that Officer Zhou?

176
00:09:58,690 --> 00:09:59,350
Yes.

177
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,240
Take it easy.

178
00:10:00,270 --> 00:10:00,840
That's her, right?

179
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,570
Take it easy.

180
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:03,790
Captain Zhou.

181
00:10:03,790 --> 00:10:05,080
Two elderly people are here to see you.

182
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:07,030
They've been waiting for you
for a long time.

183
00:10:07,030 --> 00:10:09,440
Are you Officer Zhou Mi?

184
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,460
We have something

185
00:10:12,030 --> 00:10:13,200
to discuss with you.

186
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:13,960
Could you...

187
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:14,440
No.

188
00:10:18,710 --> 00:10:19,870
-Officer Zhou.
-Zhou Mi.

189
00:10:19,870 --> 00:10:20,550
Alright.

190
00:10:20,630 --> 00:10:22,160
Zhou Mi, please hear us out.

191
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:22,790
Officer Zhou.

192
00:10:22,790 --> 00:10:24,150
-Zhou Mi.
-Officer Zhou.

193
00:10:24,150 --> 00:10:24,910
That's enough.

194
00:10:24,910 --> 00:10:25,710
Officer Zhou!

195
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:27,330
We've been waiting for you all day!

196
00:10:26,060 --> 00:10:28,270
[Police]

197
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:27,840
Officer Zhou!

198
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:28,510
Enough!

199
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:29,840
Mentor.

200
00:10:30,870 --> 00:10:32,750
Didn't you agree to take me
under your wing?

201
00:10:32,750 --> 00:10:34,390
Then you should at least
teach me something.

202
00:10:34,390 --> 00:10:35,200
I'm just a rookie.

203
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,550
You don't answer my questions.

204
00:10:36,550 --> 00:10:37,240
You don't tell me anything

205
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,390
about case developments.

206
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:39,670
I can't make sense of anything.

207
00:10:39,670 --> 00:10:41,790
I'm completely lost.
How am I supposed to learn?

208
00:10:41,790 --> 00:10:43,120
If you have any other complaints about me,

209
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,520
just say them all at once.

210
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,120
The elderly couple
at the entrance just now,

211
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:47,890
why wouldn't you even

212
00:10:47,890 --> 00:10:48,750
let them speak?

213
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,770
They might have legitimate concerns.

214
00:10:50,770 --> 00:10:52,550
They could be relatives of someone
involved in the case.

215
00:10:52,550 --> 00:10:54,810
Or they might want to provide some leads.

216
00:10:55,870 --> 00:10:57,510
If you're unhappy with my way
of handling cases,

217
00:10:57,510 --> 00:10:59,320
go find Captain Gao first thing
tomorrow morning

218
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,450
and get a new mentor.

219
00:11:01,270 --> 00:11:02,000
Also,

220
00:11:02,630 --> 00:11:04,480
don't follow me around anymore today.

221
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,480
Go home and rest!

