00:11:46,670 --> 00:11:47,400
Captain Gao.

227
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:50,200
Still studying the crime scene photos?

228
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:52,200
Found anything suspicious?

229
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:53,690
Many things.

230
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:57,070
The night of the incident,
power went out on Hesheng Street.

231
00:11:57,070 --> 00:12:00,590
[General Manager Su Muxin, missing]

232
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:59,270
Su Muxin stayed at Shi Yue's place

233
00:11:59,270 --> 00:12:00,470
for the entire night.

234
00:12:01,780 --> 00:12:03,780
He was very familiar with that room,

235
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:05,170
so logically he should have been able

236
00:12:05,170 --> 00:12:06,970
to easily restore these things.

237
00:12:09,910 --> 00:12:10,870
But,

238
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:12,670
he only took

239
00:12:12,670 --> 00:12:13,960
Shi Yue's phone,

240
00:12:14,550 --> 00:12:16,080
leaving all this evidence

241
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:16,860
untouched.

242
00:12:17,910 --> 00:12:18,840
There are contradictions

243
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,840
and illogical aspects everywhere.

244
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,290
We previously deduced

245
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:26,360
that Su Muxin and Qu Tong
were conspiring together,

246
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,670
that Qu Tong was helping Su Muxin,

247
00:12:27,670 --> 00:12:29,670
and that Su Muxin was hiding in Yunzhou.

248
00:12:29,670 --> 00:12:30,960
But now I think

249
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:33,440
our deduction was wrong.

250
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:36,840
Maybe all of Qu Tong's suspicious behavior

251
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,570
had nothing to do with Su Muxin.

252
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,550
Why do you say

253
00:12:39,550 --> 00:12:41,550
your previous deduction was wrong?

254
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,580
Qu Tong is someone

255
00:12:45,790 --> 00:12:47,120
who's extremely cautious

256
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:48,580
and doesn't trust anyone.

257
00:12:48,670 --> 00:12:50,150
I've dealt with her a few times

258
00:12:50,150 --> 00:12:51,950
and she has never told the truth.

259
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:53,000
But today

260
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,750
when she was facing Shi Yue's mother...

261
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:56,720
Say something!

262
00:12:56,750 --> 00:12:57,870
Yes, you're right.

263
00:12:58,670 --> 00:13:00,870
There was the mix of old and new grudges.

264
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,680
Her reaction was emotional.

265
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:04,670
Because I lost interest

266
00:13:04,670 --> 00:13:05,750
in him long ago.

267
00:13:08,270 --> 00:13:09,870
I think that was the real her.

268
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:12,520
Her relationship with Su Muxin

269
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:13,600
is probably

270
00:13:14,550 --> 00:13:16,550
different from what she's showing.

271
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:17,910
Without some

272
00:13:17,910 --> 00:13:18,870
special reason,

273
00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:21,080
she wouldn't help Su Muxin.

274
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,660
It's getting late.

275
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,840
You should get some rest.

276
00:13:27,750 --> 00:13:28,440
You

277
00:13:28,670 --> 00:13:30,390
stop cooping yourself up here all day!

278
00:13:30,390 --> 00:13:31,750
Go home if you need to.

279
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,270
One more thing, Captain Gao.

280
00:13:34,270 --> 00:13:35,530
Not up for discussion.

281
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:37,630
About Wu Dong,

282
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:38,550
you have to mentor him,

283
00:13:38,550 --> 00:13:40,010
whether you like it or not.

284
00:14:23,550 --> 00:14:24,360
Are you

285
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,200
there?

286
00:15:43,750 --> 00:15:46,100
[Wait for my contact]

287
