00:16:04,630 --> 00:16:05,490
Officer Zhou.

290
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:07,060
I'm Ms. Zhang.

291
00:16:07,290 --> 00:16:09,650
[Teaching Building]

292
00:16:09,270 --> 00:16:10,360
When school starts again,

293
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:11,200
we'll all be moving

294
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,330
to the new district.

295
00:16:12,750 --> 00:16:14,480
This place will be demolished.

296
00:16:14,910 --> 00:16:15,790
To be honest,

297
00:16:16,030 --> 00:16:17,690
I'm quite reluctant to leave.

298
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:19,360
This school was built

299
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:20,870
back in the 1970s.

300
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:23,000
You called

301
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:25,270
to ask about Qu Tong,

302
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:26,150
Su Muxin,

303
00:16:26,240 --> 00:16:27,790
and Hao Meili from the 1986 cohort.

304
00:16:27,790 --> 00:16:29,030
I've done my best

305
00:16:29,120 --> 00:16:29,720
to collect all the things

306
00:16:29,720 --> 00:16:30,840
they left behind

307
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:31,960
back then.

308
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:33,960
But it has been a long time.

309
00:16:34,270 --> 00:16:35,530
There's not much left.

310
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:36,080
Okay.

311
00:16:44,790 --> 00:16:46,200
Here's everything I have on them.

312
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:46,670
Okay.

313
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:51,200
[Hao Meili, Class 1, Senior 3]

314
00:16:51,250 --> 00:16:53,580
[Li Li, Class 2, Senior 3]

315
00:16:53,710 --> 00:16:54,830
[Su Muxin, Class 1, Senior 3]

316
00:16:56,600 --> 00:16:58,480
Do you have a strong impression
of Su Muxin?

317
00:16:58,480 --> 00:17:00,480
Su Muxin was the class monitor then,

318
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:01,810
with excellent grades.

319
00:17:02,210 --> 00:17:03,740
[Qu Tong, Class 1, Senior 3]

320
00:17:02,630 --> 00:17:04,030
He was from Chen Village,

321
00:17:04,600 --> 00:17:06,080
far from the county town.

322
00:17:06,320 --> 00:17:07,960
I remember he only had his mother,

323
00:17:07,960 --> 00:17:08,720
no father.

324
00:17:08,960 --> 00:17:09,560
Thank you.

325
00:17:10,880 --> 00:17:12,740
There were no highways back then.

326
00:17:12,920 --> 00:17:14,000
Going home

327
00:17:14,109 --> 00:17:15,880
would take him an entire night.

328
00:17:16,200 --> 00:17:17,349
So at that time,

329
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:19,180
he lived in the dormitory.

330
00:17:19,349 --> 00:17:20,270
In the 1980s,

331
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:22,200
getting into college was very difficult.

332
00:17:22,200 --> 00:17:24,260
So the whole village was proud of him.

333
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:39,920
Ms. Zhang, I'm innocent.

334
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:41,640
In today's class meeting,

335
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:43,350
although I apologized,

336
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:45,000
it wasn't sincere.

337
00:17:45,350 --> 00:17:47,030
I really didn't do that.

338
00:17:48,550 --> 00:17:49,400
It has been

339
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:51,030
over ten years.

340
00:17:52,590 --> 00:17:54,190
But I still can't get over it.

341
00:17:55,640 --> 00:17:57,200
I didn't handle it well back then.

342
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:58,750
I want Qu Tong to apologize!

343
00:17:58,170 --> 00:18:01,760
[1986]

344
00:18:03,960 --> 00:18:04,640
Hao Meili.

345
00:18:05,270 --> 00:18:06,680
I want her to apologize.

346
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:19,880
I'm sorry.

347
00:18:43,830 --> 00:18:45,490
What kind of person
is Qu Tong?

348
00:18:45,550 --> 00:18:47,270
In my impression, she was
very introverted,

349
00:18:47,270 --> 00:18:48,000
quiet,

350
00:18:48,960 --> 00:18:50,400
and strictly supervised by her family.

351
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,790
So she never attended

352
00:18:51,830 --> 00:18:53,240
any gatherings with classmates.

353
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:54,570
She didn't talk much,

354
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:56,540
and basically had no friends.

355
00:18:57,200 --> 00:18:58,110
Vixen.

356
00:18:58,310 --> 00:18:59,970
The vixen of No. 1 High School.

357
00:19:02,550 --> 00:19:03,550
But she was very smart,

358
00:19:03,550 --> 00:19:04,880
with excellent grades.

359
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:07,000
Before Hao Meili transferred
to our school,

360
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:08,860
she always ranked first in exams.

361
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:10,830
After that incident happened,

362
00:19:10,960 --> 00:19:13,020
it had a huge emotional impact on her,

363
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:16,280
even affecting her academic performance.

364
00:19:16,510 --> 00:19:18,040
But she recovered quickly,

365
00:19:18,270 --> 00:19:19,240
and eventually

366
00:19:19,270 --> 00:19:20,590
got into college successfully.

367
00:19:20,590 --> 00:19:21,830
So I think

368
00:19:23,070 --> 00:19:25,330
she might appear fragile on the outside,

369
00:19:25,400 --> 00:19:26,400
but actually

370
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:28,820
she was a very resilient girl.

371
00:19:31,550 --> 00:19:32,270
Well,

372
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:34,880
was Qu Tong responsible for

373
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:37,140
the bullying of Hao Meili?

374
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:38,740
There's no way

375
00:19:38,740 --> 00:19:40,470
to verify this matter anymore.

376
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:42,790
But I don't think it was her.

377
00:19:43,350 --> 00:19:44,610
Was Su Muxin involved?

378
00:19:45,630 --> 00:19:46,830
I'm not sure about that.

379
00:19:46,830 --> 00:19:47,590
Qu Tong seems

380
00:19:47,610 --> 00:19:48,690
a bit pitiful.

381
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:49,680
Indeed.

382
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:51,900
You feel sorry for her?

383
00:19:52,440 --> 00:19:53,880
Do you know what she is?

384
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:54,680
What?

385
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:57,830
The vixen of No. 1 High School.

386
00:19:58,880 --> 00:19:59,790
Vixen.

387
00:19:59,830 --> 00:20:01,150
Vixen.

388
00:20:01,350 --> 00:20:02,130
You feel sorry for her?

389
00:20:02,130 --> 00:20:03,190
That vixen.

390
00:20:04,350 --> 00:20:05,070
Feel sorry?

391
00:20:05,090 --> 00:20:06,480
Why feel sorry for her?

392
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:08,110
She's just a vixen.

393
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:20,230
[Sanjie Restaurant]

394
00:20:18,590 --> 00:20:20,120
Maybe we missed something.

395
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:21,640
Otherwise we shouldn't

396
00:20:21,640 --> 00:20:23,300
have failed to catch Su Muxin.

397
00:20:25,380 --> 00:20:26,200
So you called me here

398
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:28,130
to see if there are any other leads?

399
00:20:28,250 --> 00:20:31,000
[Sanjie Restaurant]

400
00:20:34,990 --> 00:20:38,230
[Open]

401
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:40,080
Mr. Zhang, look here.

402
00:20:40,830 --> 00:20:41,590
From here you can see

403
00:20:41,590 --> 00:20:43,050
our car across the street.

404
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:45,310
Qu Tong must have spotted

405
00:20:45,310 --> 00:20:46,720
that we were following her

406
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:48,200
and passed the message to Su Muxin.

407
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:49,330
It must be like that.

408
00:20:49,550 --> 00:20:50,790
Our car was parked right over there.

409
00:20:50,650 --> 00:20:53,220
[Sanjie Restaurant]

410
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:55,000
Besides Qu Tong,

411
00:20:55,030 --> 00:20:56,880
was Su Muxin close

412
00:20:57,110 --> 00:20:58,640
with any other classmates?

413
00:20:59,590 --> 00:21:01,070
I heard from students

414
00:21:01,090 --> 00:21:02,080
in his year

415
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:03,770
that after Su Muxin got into college,

416
00:21:03,770 --> 00:21:05,640
he cut off contact
with his former classmates.

417
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:06,640
Later, someone

418
00:21:06,750 --> 00:21:08,110
ran into him in Yunzhou.

419
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:11,400
It was said he worked
at the Industry and Commerce Bureau

420
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:13,260
and had become a senior official.

421
00:21:17,410 --> 00:21:18,270
At that time, Qu Tong's car

422
00:21:18,270 --> 00:21:19,350
was parked right here.

423
00:21:19,350 --> 00:21:20,410
After she went out,

424
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,450
she got something from her car.

425
00:21:22,790 --> 00:21:23,510
We didn't notice

426
00:21:23,510 --> 00:21:24,770
anything suspicious.

427
00:21:25,110 --> 00:21:25,830
After getting off the car,

428
00:21:25,830 --> 00:21:27,030
she walked along this road

429
00:21:27,030 --> 00:21:27,960
straight ahead,

430
00:21:28,550 --> 00:21:29,950
never leaving our sight.

431
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:33,330
Where exactly did things go wrong?

432
00:21:39,110 --> 00:21:39,830
Details.

433
00:21:41,030 --> 00:21:42,000
There must be some details

434
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:43,060
that we've missed.

435
00:21:48,720 --> 00:21:49,270
Hello.

436
00:21:49,010 --> 00:21:50,930
[Yunzhou Trading Company]

437
00:21:50,240 --> 00:21:50,970
I'm here to see Mr. Li.

438
00:21:50,970 --> 00:21:54,700
[Yunzhou Trading Company]

439
00:21:52,350 --> 00:21:54,480
Mr. Li, Officer Zhou is here to see you.

440
00:21:55,270 --> 00:21:56,000
Please come in.

441
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:57,200
Officer Zhou from Dongjiang, right?

442
00:21:57,200 --> 00:21:57,790
Hello, Mr. Li.

443
00:21:57,790 --> 00:21:59,250
Hello, please have a seat.

444
00:22:00,310 --> 00:22:01,680
I'm here today to ask you

445
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:03,310
about someone.

446
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:04,060
About whom?

447
00:22:04,110 --> 00:22:04,880
Su Muxin.

448
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:07,320
Mr. Su from Zhuo'er Jewelry?

449
00:22:08,310 --> 00:22:09,280
In 1994,

450
00:22:09,310 --> 00:22:10,240
Su Muxin was transferred back

451
00:22:10,240 --> 00:22:12,480
to serve as deputy section chief
at Yunzhou Industry and Commerce Bureau.

452
00:22:12,480 --> 00:22:13,070
At that time,

453
00:22:13,070 --> 00:22:14,270
you hadn't resigned
to go into business yet.

454
00:22:14,270 --> 00:22:15,510
You were his superior,

455
00:22:15,510 --> 00:22:16,240
weren't you?

456
00:22:16,550 --> 00:22:17,070
Yes.

457
00:22:17,930 --> 00:22:18,720
But after he married Qu Tong,

458
00:22:18,720 --> 00:22:19,480
he resigned

459
00:22:19,510 --> 00:22:21,350
not long after.

460
00:22:21,640 --> 00:22:23,440
Later I also went into business.

461
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:25,360
We didn't interact much.

462
00:22:26,590 --> 00:22:27,720
You know Qu Tong too?

463
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:30,370
Just a coincidence.

464
00:22:30,830 --> 00:22:31,880
They reunited

465
00:22:31,920 --> 00:22:32,920
at the Industry and Commerce Bureau.

466
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:34,180
I was there at the time.

467
00:22:35,400 --> 00:22:35,920
Director Li.

468
00:22:35,660 --> 00:22:39,250
[1994]

469
00:22:36,030 --> 00:22:36,490
Come in.

470
00:22:40,160 --> 00:22:41,240
Could you please check

471
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:41,920
if their paperwork

472
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:43,120
is missing anything?

473
00:22:43,480 --> 00:22:44,550
This is similar to the case

474
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:45,350
you handled last time.

475
00:22:45,350 --> 00:22:45,680
Sure.

476
00:22:47,270 --> 00:22:47,960
Su Muxin.

477
00:23:01,740 --> 00:23:03,270
I wrote you many letters,

478
00:23:03,780 --> 00:23:05,040
but you never replied.

479
00:23:09,120 --> 00:23:09,920
I even called the school

480
00:23:09,920 --> 00:23:11,000
to confirm

481
00:23:11,760 --> 00:23:13,420
that the address was correct.

482
00:23:15,350 --> 00:23:15,950
Is that so?

483
00:23:19,760 --> 00:23:20,820
It doesn't matter.

484
00:23:22,700 --> 00:23:24,560
The good thing is we've met again.

485
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:28,890
Tong.

486
00:23:31,200 --> 00:23:32,130
We should go now.

487
00:23:35,310 --> 00:23:36,310
Section Chief Su.

488
00:23:36,910 --> 00:23:38,110
About the paperwork,

489
00:23:38,310 --> 00:23:39,840
I'll leave it in your hands.

490
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:40,850
You're welcome.

491
00:23:43,730 --> 00:23:47,060
[General Office]

492
00:23:43,840 --> 00:23:44,740
Tong, let's go.

493
00:23:50,330 --> 00:23:51,530
Since you're so busy,

494
00:23:52,810 --> 00:23:54,340
I won't bother you anymore.

495
00:24:02,420 --> 00:24:03,750
This is my pager number.

496
00:24:04,550 --> 00:24:05,550
I'll be going now.

497
00:24:10,130 --> 00:24:11,240
[Announcement Board
of Yunzhou Industry and Commerce Bureau]

498
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:19,770
This high school classmate of yours

499
00:24:19,770 --> 00:24:21,300
is Qu Lijun's daughter?

500
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:22,730
Their family

501
00:24:24,060 --> 00:24:25,160
is quite well-off.

502
00:24:26,230 --> 00:24:28,060
He made his fortune in Guangdong.

503
00:24:28,060 --> 00:24:30,220
A couple of years ago, he took over
a factory in the county,

504
00:24:30,220 --> 00:24:32,100
specializing in jewelry processing.

505
00:24:32,100 --> 00:24:33,040
It's going quite well.

506
00:24:33,040 --> 00:24:33,620
And

507
00:24:33,650 --> 00:24:35,350
they've even landed a contract

508
00:24:35,350 --> 00:24:37,240
with that high-end brand Jinfeng
from Guangdong.

509
00:24:37,240 --> 00:24:38,350
They're really expanding.

510
00:24:38,350 --> 00:24:38,950
That's why

511
00:24:39,130 --> 00:24:41,260
they're applying for land to scale up.

512
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:43,470
Take a good look at this.

513
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:53,400
Section Chief Su.

514
00:25:05,210 --> 00:25:12,480
[Yunzhou Trading Company]

515
00:25:05,290 --> 00:25:06,690
I'm sorry, Officer Zhou.

516
00:25:06,750 --> 00:25:08,210
I couldn't be of much help.

517
00:25:08,640 --> 00:25:09,500
About his case,

518
00:25:09,890 --> 00:25:11,620
my knowledge is quite limited.

519
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:14,310
What do you

520
00:25:14,790 --> 00:25:16,270
think of Su Muxin?

521
00:25:18,550 --> 00:25:20,270
Speaking of Su Muxin,

522
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:24,840
I think he's destined for great things.

523
00:25:25,030 --> 00:25:26,630
He's decisive in his actions

524
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:27,770
and at the same time,

525
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:30,220
he's hardly influenced by emotions.

526
00:25:30,640 --> 00:25:31,770
He's very rational.

527
00:25:32,490 --> 00:25:33,090
Of course,

528
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:35,170
from another perspective,

529
00:25:35,510 --> 00:25:37,710
some might find him a bit cold-hearted.

530
00:25:38,950 --> 00:25:39,560
I see.

531
00:25:40,350 --> 00:25:41,310
Thanks for your cooperation.

532
00:25:41,310 --> 00:25:42,040
My pleasure.

533
00:25:42,170 --> 00:25:42,960
Please don't see me out.

534
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:43,560
Take care.

535
00:25:53,960 --> 00:25:55,590
Where did we go wrong?

536
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:56,850
Otherwise we shouldn't

537
00:25:56,850 --> 00:25:58,510
have failed to catch Su Muxin.

538
00:25:59,370 --> 00:26:01,230
It's fine. Let's head back first.

539
00:26:18,070 --> 00:26:18,640
Hello.

540
00:26:19,830 --> 00:26:21,290
Okay, I'll be right there.

541
00:26:24,270 --> 00:26:24,640
Mentor,

542
00:26:24,640 --> 00:26:26,500
I think there's one possibility.

543
00:26:26,600 --> 00:26:27,680
Qu Tong and Su Muxin

544
00:26:27,720 --> 00:26:28,440
did actually arrange

545
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:29,920
to meet at Sanjie Restaurant.

546
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:30,960
But she discovered early on

547
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:32,490
that we were following her.

548
00:26:32,590 --> 00:26:33,790
You were inside the restaurant then,

549
00:26:33,790 --> 00:26:35,450
while I was watching at the entrance.

550
00:26:35,450 --> 00:26:36,550
When Qu Tong left,

551
00:26:36,590 --> 00:26:38,450
her movements were a bit strange.

552
00:26:39,630 --> 00:26:41,830
But only now do I realize what was wrong.

553
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:43,000
After she went out,

554
00:26:43,020 --> 00:26:45,020
she went to her car to get something.

555
00:26:47,110 --> 00:26:49,040
There was a clear unlocking sound.

556
00:26:52,510 --> 00:26:53,480
But when

557
00:26:53,510 --> 00:26:55,000
we came back with her,

558
00:26:58,440 --> 00:26:59,240
she made

559
00:26:59,270 --> 00:27:00,730
a fake unlocking gesture,

560
00:27:01,680 --> 00:27:03,080
with no unlocking sound.

561
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:05,440
Goodbye.

562
00:27:07,310 --> 00:27:09,160
She wasn't getting something earlier.

563
00:27:09,160 --> 00:27:10,890
She was just unlocking the car.

564
00:27:12,680 --> 00:27:14,310
If we follow this reasoning,

565
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:16,440
when we were following her,

566
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:17,750
her nervous expression

567
00:27:17,750 --> 00:27:18,950
and looking back at us

568
00:27:19,160 --> 00:27:21,060
wasn't because she feared
us following her,

569
00:27:21,060 --> 00:27:22,790
but she feared we wouldn't follow her.

570
00:27:22,790 --> 00:27:23,350
Right.

571
00:27:24,230 --> 00:27:24,830
I suspect

572
00:27:24,880 --> 00:27:26,140
that during this time,

573
00:27:26,320 --> 00:27:27,680
Su Muxin had already hidden

574
00:27:27,680 --> 00:27:29,280
in the trunk of Qu Tong's car.

575
00:28:11,580 --> 00:28:15,410
[Restroom]

576
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:30,510
Hello.

577
00:28:30,550 --> 00:28:31,810
Are you here for a meal?

578
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:36,780
[Restroom,
Caution, Wet Floor]

579
00:28:36,960 --> 00:28:39,870
[Friendly Reminder,
Caution, Wet Floor]

580
00:28:58,680 --> 00:28:59,480
